    dc:description "Figure 12. Synapomorphic characters of Zethus (Zethusculus) A habitus of Z. jurinei B close-up of female clypeus of Z. mexicanus C tegula of Z. mexicanus; arrowheads indicate length of interruprion on raised margin D male flagellum of Z. mexicanus. Scale bars: 1.0 mm." ;
